import React ,{ useState}from 'react'

function Login() {
  return (
    <form action="">
    <label htmlFor="email">Email</label>
        <input type="email"
        id='email'
        placeholder='E-mail' />
    <label htmlFor="Password">Password</label>
    <input type="password"
    id='password'
    placeholder='Enter Password' />
    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
  )
}

export default Login
